{"tid":1913990,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[發達攻略] 發現啲有錢仔都有個共通點 !","createTime":"2020-03-07T08:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T14:09:28.000Z","uid":107157,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"31cf657ec77ae34d08a765f9453ce0f59bcab832","tid":1913990,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:17:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係又白又大隻又有肌肉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1。有錢仔日日唔洗返工唔洗做野，大把時間去做gym。你一日做得2個鐘，佢隨時一日做10個鐘都得。自己就成身肌肉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2。有錢仔最鐘意就係食女，多肌肉自己多女自動埋身，扑野都輕鬆啲。<br />\n<br />\n3。你話唔係wor，做地盤既都好大隻喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係做地盤日曬夜曬，大隻完都變左舊黑炭啦，有錢仔就唔同，唔洗曬，日日又有閒錢買護膚品用，隨時白過隻鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係窮係富我一眼就睇得到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方法就講左比你聽，把唔把握到就靠你自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d58b556202e0f33acc3a4c0031d60242ce26fcf","tid":1913990,"uid":27362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31cf657ec77ae34d08a765f9453ce0f59bcab832","tid":1913990,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:17:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係又白又大隻又有肌肉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1。有錢仔日日唔洗返工唔洗做野，大把時間去做gym。你一日做得2個鐘，佢隨時一日做10個鐘都得。自己就成身肌肉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2。有錢仔最鐘意就係食女，多肌肉自己多女自動埋身，扑野都輕鬆啲。<br />\n<br />\n3。你話唔係wor，做地盤既都好大隻喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係做地盤日曬夜曬，大隻完都變左舊黑炭啦，有錢仔就唔同，唔洗曬，日日又有閒錢買護膚品用，隨時白過隻鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係窮係富我一眼就睇得到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />